    "feat": {
        "name": "Rally Support",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You often rely on the local populace for supplies and shelter. Once per day, you can attempt a check to Request or Coerce against an easy DC for your level when speaking with someone who is a non-hostile, long-term resident of your favored location. On a success, choose one of the following to obtain. \n* A nonmagical item of your level or lower\n* A safe place to shelter for 24 hours\n* 3 days' worth of food and water for you and up to 5 allies",
        "level": 8,
